# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ML Model Files
# stress_model.pt (254 MB) and tokenizer.pkl are LARGE.
# Use Git LFS to track them, or exclude them from Git
# and share them via Google Drive / cloud storage.
#
# To include via Git LFS, run:
#   git lfs install
#   git lfs track "ml_service/stress_model.pt"
#   git lfs track "ml_service/tokenizer.pkl"
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
ml_service/stress_model.pt
ml_service/tokenizer.pkl

# Old LSTM model files (replaced by DistilBERT)
ml_service/model.pkl
ml_service/sequence_config.pkl
*.h5
*.pb
model_weights/

